name: Booking a service with >24h duration - professional's place

steps.name: Input search text and press Enter
$("app-search form input") set value("Dynamic Response Assistant (slttkwt)")
Verify that the search result is correct
$("app-search-result ion-card-content app-service-link") should have(text "Dynamic Response Assistant (slttkwt)")
Verify that the service data is correct

$("app-service-widget") should have(text "The first rule of space travel kids is always check out distress beacons. Nine out of ten times it's a ship full of dead aliens and a bunch of free shit! One out of ten times it's a deadly trap, but... I'm ready to roll those dice! So comes snow after fire, and even dragons have their endings.")
